### What about this f... linux ###

When you get access on a new linux machine, you like to know what is on it...
this is a little tool to diagnose your box


- Create a setup.py file to install easily the package
http://foobar.lu/wp/2012/05/13/a-comprehensive-step-through-python-packaging-a-k-a-setup-scripts/


